00:34:11.599 --> 00:34:14.790
labor pains upon a woman, you will

00:34:14.800 --> 00:34:17.669
see a great acceleration, even more, come

00:34:17.679 --> 00:34:20.310
this fall around September the 21st, or

00:34:20.320 --> 00:34:23.109
whatever it is, when Rosh Hashanah starts. I'm

00:34:23.119 --> 00:34:25.349
telling you all, it's time to open your

00:34:25.359 --> 00:34:27.589
eyes. We're running out of time. 'Well,

00:34:27.599 --> 00:34:29.109
how many more years do we have,

00:34:29.119 --> 00:34:31.190
Brandon? Do you think we have ten

00:34:31.190 --> 00:34:31.200
years?'I

00:34:31.200 --> 00:34:34.149
don't know. No man knows the day

00:34:34.149 --> 00:34:34.159
or

00:34:34.159 --> 00:34:36.069
the hour when the Son of Man returns.

00:34:36.079 --> 00:34:37.430
Nobody knows, you understand? That's

00:34:37.440 --> 00:34:38.950
what the Bible says, right? Not even

00:34:38.960 --> 00:34:42.069
Him. So, but we can see the signs of the

00:34:42.079 --> 00:34:43.430
times and what the fig tree is

00:34:43.430 --> 00:34:43.440
doing

00:34:43.440 --> 00:34:44.869
with Israel and all these other things.

00:34:44.879 --> 00:34:47.270
We can see it all around us. As you look,

00:34:47.280 --> 00:34:50.310
as the day approaches, look around

00:34:50.320 --> 00:34:52.389
you. Take your head out of the sand and

00:34:52.399 --> 00:34:56.470
look around you.

00:34:56.480 --> 00:34:58.470
How much more will we see? I pray,

00:34:58.480 --> 00:35:00.310
I hope we don't see the plague.

00:35:00.320 --> 00:35:01.829
I hope we don't see some of these

00:35:01.839 --> 00:35:03.270
things. But the Lord told me we're

00:35:03.280 --> 00:35:06.310
going to see some things.

00:35:06.320 --> 00:35:08.230
He said, 'Brandon, there'll be a lot of

00:35:08.240 --> 00:35:11.510
people who think it's

00:35:11.510 --> 00:35:11.520
Ichabod,

00:35:11.520 --> 00:35:13.990
that I've departed.

00:35:14.000 --> 00:35:16.470
This is not

00:35:16.470 --> 00:35:16.480
Ichabod.

00:35:16.480 --> 00:35:18.470
This is not Ichabod. But when people go

00:35:18.480 --> 00:35:20.550
through trying times and they go through

00:35:20.560 --> 00:35:22.790
hard things,'He said, 'they automatically

00:35:22.800 --> 00:35:24.710
just go, "Well, God has abandoned me. He

00:35:24.720 --> 00:35:26.390
doesn't love me. I'm going through all

00:35:26.390 --> 00:35:26.400
this."The

00:35:26.400 --> 00:35:28.470
refining fire is hard

00:35:28.480 --> 00:35:30.550
sometimes, folks.'But you go, 'Well, I

00:35:30.560 --> 00:35:31.829
don't want to go through any of these

00:35:31.839 --> 00:35:34.069
hard times. This is really hard. What's

00:35:34.079 --> 00:35:36.310
going on?'So, 'God has abandoned,

00:35:36.310 --> 00:35:36.320
Ichabod

00:35:36.320 --> 00:35:38.710
has happened.'But He said, 'I'll never

00:35:38.720 --> 00:35:40.470
leave you and I'll never forsake you. Lo,

00:35:40.470 --> 00:35:40.480
unto

00:35:40.480 --> 00:35:41.910
the end of the earth, I'll be with

00:35:41.920 --> 00:35:44.069
you always.'But many people will say,

00:35:44.079 --> 00:35:46.710
'This is an Ichabod what's

00:35:46.710 --> 00:35:46.720
coming,'when

00:35:46.720 --> 00:35:48.710
you see the great shakings of things.

00:35:48.720 --> 00:35:49.990
Well, we don't have to go through all

00:35:50.000 --> 00:35:52.630
that. Some of the greatest ministers

00:35:52.640 --> 00:35:54.069
we've ever known in the past—and I'll

00:35:54.079 --> 00:35:55.910
say it again and say it

00:35:55.910 --> 00:35:55.920
again—they

00:35:55.920 --> 00:35:57.750
went through some very hard trials, the

00:35:57.760 --> 00:35:59.670
Great Depression. They went through the

00:35:59.680 --> 00:36:01.030
Great Depression. There

00:36:01.040 --> 00:36:05.910
were some really godly people,

00:36:05.920 --> 00:36:07.349
when you go back and you look

00:36:07.359 --> 00:36:09.190
at the old-time movies and the way they

00:36:09.200 --> 00:36:10.550
presented themselves, and they didn't

00:36:10.560 --> 00:36:13.910
even sleep in the same bed.

00:36:13.920 --> 00:36:16.550
I Love Lucy was one of

00:36:16.550 --> 00:36:16.560
them—two

00:36:16.560 --> 00:36:19.750
separate rooms. But now, they

00:36:19.760 --> 00:36:21.829
basically do it on TV now, and you're

00:36:21.839 --> 00:36:23.109
looking at it going, 'What is going on?

00:36:23.119 --> 00:36:25.349
There's no morals. They got morals like

00:36:25.359 --> 00:36:27.910
a

00:36:27.910 --> 00:36:27.920
cat.'And

00:36:27.920 --> 00:36:29.589
there's nobody out there living

00:36:29.599 --> 00:36:32.630
righteous and holy. But

00:36:32.640 --> 00:36:35.589
sin has become so acceptable, and

00:36:35.599 --> 00:36:39.510
as it's become more up like this

00:36:39.520 --> 00:36:41.750
and the sinometers, whatever, the

00:36:41.760 --> 00:36:43.510
church has accepted it. Well, we have a

00:36:43.520 --> 00:36:44.870
little bit of a gray area, and we try to

00:36:44.880 --> 00:36:46.069
accept a little bit more instead of

00:36:46.079 --> 00:36:49.990
being repulsed. If the people in the

00:36:49.990 --> 00:36:50.000
1920s

00:36:50.000 --> 00:36:52.230
saw what we're

00:36:52.240 --> 00:36:53.990
watching right now, they would blush.

00:36:54.000 --> 00:36:55.430
Our

00:36:55.430 --> 00:36:55.440
great-grandparents,

00:36:55.440 --> 00:36:56.950
they would blush. They

00:36:56.960 --> 00:36:59.910
would go, 'Oh my goodness, this is like

00:36:59.910 --> 00:36:59.920
Gomorrah

00:36:59.920 --> 00:37:02.630
up in here.'But what has

00:37:02.640 --> 00:37:05.829
become acceptable to us now was

00:37:05.839 --> 00:37:08.630
repulsive to our

00:37:08.640 --> 00:37:10.630
great-grandparents.

00:37:10.640 --> 00:37:12.950
But it's okay now. But the church even

00:37:12.960 --> 00:37:14.390
embraces it: 'Oh, it's all right, you

00:37:14.400 --> 00:37:18.550
know, to

00:37:18.550 --> 00:37:18.560
a degree.'But

00:37:18.560 --> 00:37:19.829
I'm trying to tell you, a cleaning

00:37:19.839 --> 00:37:21.430
of the house. And that's why, whenever

00:37:21.440 --> 00:37:22.950
people go through hard times, they don't

00:37:22.960 --> 00:37:24.870
have no backbone,

00:37:24.880 --> 00:37:26.790
and a great shaking to awaken is coming.

00:37:26.800 --> 00:37:28.069
And the body of Christ is going to see

00:37:28.079 --> 00:37:29.910
brush arbor churches like we've never

00:37:29.920 --> 00:37:32.069
seen before. And there will be a major

00:37:32.079 --> 00:37:33.750
move of God like we've never seen

00:37:33.760 --> 00:37:36.470
before. He's coming back for a bride

00:37:36.480 --> 00:37:38.950
without spot or wrinkle

00:37:38.960 --> 00:37:42.230
that's not in bed with the world, that

00:37:42.240 --> 00:37:44.390
has one foot in the world and one foot

00:37:44.400 --> 00:37:46.310
in the church, and we're riding the fence

00:37:46.320 --> 00:37:50.310
going, 'It's okay.'It's not okay.

00:37:50.320 --> 00:37:51.589
And there'll be a lot of people that

00:37:51.599 --> 00:37:52.870
just turn me off right now: 'I don't want

00:37:52.880 --> 00:37:56.310
to listen to him. Bye.'But I can't

00:37:56.310 --> 00:37:56.320
tell—you

00:37:56.320 --> 00:37:58.470
can't say that I didn't warn you for

00:37:58.480 --> 00:38:00.630
what's coming.

00:38:00.640 --> 00:38:02.550
You can't say, 'I didn't sound the alarm

00:38:02.560 --> 00:38:04.550
as loud as I could to tell you what's

00:38:04.550 --> 00:38:04.560
coming.'Great

00:38:04.560 --> 00:38:09.829
deception is coming.

00:38:09.839 --> 00:38:12.870
People you trust on a regular basis

00:38:12.880 --> 00:38:14.390
in churches are going to be

00:38:14.400 --> 00:38:15.910
exposed.

00:38:15.920 --> 00:38:18.230
There's darkness behind the pulpits, and

00:38:18.240 --> 00:38:20.390
the Lord's cleaning house. Judgment

00:38:20.400 --> 00:38:23.270
begins in the house of the Lord first.

00:38:23.280 --> 00:38:25.990
And people don't want to hear that. But

00:38:26.000 --> 00:38:28.870
you think you can live on the fence,

00:38:28.880 --> 00:38:31.430
party during the week, do all what

00:38:31.430 --> 00:38:31.440
you're

00:38:31.440 --> 00:38:33.589
doing, and then go to church and act

00:38:33.599 --> 00:38:35.589
holy on the weekend? 'Well, grace is

00:38:35.599 --> 00:38:38.150
covering it.'But we don't abuse it, and

00:38:38.160 --> 00:38:40.630
we don't act like the world. If you had

00:38:40.640 --> 00:38:43.430
a lineup and you were standing in a

00:38:43.440 --> 00:38:45.030
lineup, folks, and you were there and

00:38:45.040 --> 00:38:46.310
you said, 'Which one's the

00:38:46.320 --> 00:38:47.430
Christian? Which one's

00:38:47.430 --> 00:38:47.440
the world?'could

00:38:47.440 --> 00:38:51.109
you pick out the Christian?

00:38:51.119 --> 00:38:53.030
Is their countenance the same

00:38:53.040 --> 00:38:56.790
as the heathen?

00:38:56.800 --> 00:38:58.790
It's time to arise and shine, for the

00:38:58.800 --> 00:39:01.030
light has come and the glory of the Lord

00:39:01.040 --> 00:39:03.589
is risen upon you. It's time to be that

00:39:03.599 --> 00:39:06.310
salt and be that light, that when people

00:39:06.320 --> 00:39:07.829
are coming and they're seeing all these

00:39:07.839 --> 00:39:10.470
times of great shaking around us, that we

00:39:10.480 --> 00:39:12.790
have those catcher's mitts on and they're

00:39:12.800 --> 00:39:15.829
coming in hot. The Lord said, 'When all

00:39:15.839 --> 00:39:17.750
this hell's about to come on the earth

00:39:17.760 --> 00:39:20.150
and all this great shaking, Brandon, for

00:39:20.160 --> 00:39:21.990
I'm going to shake the world one last

00:39:22.000 --> 00:39:24.470
time, a major shaking is going to come

00:39:24.480 --> 00:39:26.150
one last time, and there's

00:39:26.160 --> 00:39:27.589
going to be the greatest harvest of

00:39:27.599 --> 00:39:30.230
souls, for the harvest is plentiful, and

00:39:30.240 --> 00:39:32.550
the laborers are few. Who will help me

00:39:32.560 --> 00:39:34.790
bring in the harvest?'He said to me,

00:39:34.800 --> 00:39:37.109
'Who will help me be the

00:39:37.119 --> 00:39:38.950
voice in these last days to bring in the

00:39:38.960 --> 00:39:42.710
harvest?'There

00:39:42.720 --> 00:39:44.630
is a heaven to gain and a hell to

00:39:44.640 --> 00:39:46.470
shun, ladies and gentlemen. And

00:39:46.480 --> 00:39:48.310
it's time to shun hell and

00:39:48.320 --> 00:39:50.950
populate heaven. We've got to get on our

00:39:50.960 --> 00:39:55.270
knees and cry out for a revival,

00:39:55.280 --> 00:39:57.750
an awakening unto God. That's the only

00:39:57.760 --> 00:39:59.270
thing that's ever going to save America.

00:39:59.280 --> 00:40:01.190
Like Sister Billie always says, 'Brandon,

00:40:01.200 --> 00:40:03.510
the only thing that is going to save

00:40:03.520 --> 00:40:05.670
America is not just revival, but an

00:40:05.680 --> 00:40:09.430
awakening unto God.'Not Trump.

00:40:09.440 --> 00:40:12.150
Trump's not going to save America. JD

00:40:12.160 --> 00:40:15.190
Vance is not going to save America.

00:40:15.190 --> 00:40:15.200
The

00:40:15.200 --> 00:40:17.910
Republican party in the Senate and

00:40:17.920 --> 00:40:20.150
the House, a great majority is not going

00:40:20.160 --> 00:40:22.550
to save America.

00:40:22.560 --> 00:40:25.270
I don't care what politician you think's

00:40:25.280 --> 00:40:27.190
going to save America. There's no

00:40:27.200 --> 00:40:29.270
politician that's ever going to save

00:40:29.280 --> 00:40:31.190
America.

00:40:31.200 --> 00:40:32.790
The only one that's ever going to save

00:40:32.800 --> 00:40:37.990
America is the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:40:38.000 --> 00:40:40.550
It's time to repent and turn back to

00:40:40.560 --> 00:40:43.750
God.

00:40:43.760 --> 00:40:46.230
When you see all these things, my

00:40:46.240 --> 00:40:48.550
heart weeps for the people and for what

00:40:48.560 --> 00:40:50.310
I've seen, for the great earthquakes

00:40:50.320 --> 00:40:52.230
that I've seen in British Columbia and

00:40:52.240 --> 00:40:54.550
all across California. I've seen

00:40:54.560 --> 00:40:57.430
great shakings,

00:40:57.440 --> 00:41:00.309
and it alarms me

00:41:00.309 --> 00:41:00.319
when

00:41:00.319 --> 00:41:02.390
I see the volcanoes and the

00:41:02.400 --> 00:41:04.470
fish dying and all these things, and the

00:41:04.480 --> 00:41:06.470
plagues and all this stuff. What will it

00:41:06.480 --> 00:41:08.069
take to wake people up out of their

00:41:08.079 --> 00:41:11.670
slumber? How many altar

00:41:11.670 --> 00:41:11.680
calls are we giving?

00:41:11.680 --> 00:41:13.670
When will we get our eyes off of

00:41:13.680 --> 00:41:15.589
growing big ministry and jets and

00:41:15.599 --> 00:41:17.670
planes, all the things, to tell

00:41:17.680 --> 00:41:19.670
people, 'It's time to repent and get your

00:41:19.680 --> 00:41:21.349
heart right for Jesus'? How many

00:41:21.349 --> 00:41:21.359
altar

00:41:21.359 --> 00:41:23.349
calls are we giving? How many people are

00:41:23.359 --> 00:41:25.670
we leading to Christ? I was

00:41:25.680 --> 00:41:27.670
so excited this week that Braden

00:41:27.680 --> 00:41:29.349
and Diana were doing the numbers. We've

00:41:29.359 --> 00:41:31.589
led several hundred people to Jesus this

00:41:31.599 --> 00:41:33.510
week.

00:41:33.520 --> 00:41:36.790
And I thought, 'That's not

00:41:36.790 --> 00:41:36.800
enough.'But

00:41:36.800 --> 00:41:40.309
I'm thankful for the beginning.

00:41:40.319 --> 00:41:41.910
You know, we gave out—I don't know how many

00:41:41.920 --> 00:41:44.309
Bibles this week. It's to the point

00:41:44.319 --> 00:41:45.589
where Diana said, 'My hands are

00:41:45.599 --> 00:41:49.829
tired, Braden.'I said, 'Praise God.

00:41:49.839 --> 00:41:51.589
People are hungry. People are

00:41:51.589 --> 00:41:51.599
desperate.'A

00:41:51.599 --> 00:41:53.190
man from China reached out

00:41:53.200 --> 00:41:54.870
to us, said, 'I got born again watching

00:41:54.880 --> 00:41:58.150
your broadcast today.'Our China channel

00:41:58.160 --> 00:42:00.150
is exploding with people

00:42:00.160 --> 00:42:01.910
through our AI thing we're doing.

00:42:01.920 --> 00:42:04.069
And South Korea—we led so many

00:42:04.079 --> 00:42:05.990
people in South Korea to Jesus this

00:42:06.000 --> 00:42:09.030
week. The Lord said, 'Brandon, I have not

00:42:09.040 --> 00:42:10.710
forgotten the Asian people. I'm going to

00:42:10.720 --> 00:42:14.550
visit them in even a greater wave.

00:42:14.560 --> 00:42:16.230
I've not forgotten the people of South

00:42:16.240 --> 00:42:18.230
Korea. I've not forgotten the people of

00:42:18.240 --> 00:42:19.750
Asia.

00:42:19.760 --> 00:42:21.750
For there's going to be a major harvest

00:42:21.760 --> 00:42:24.630
of souls in Asia.'And He said, 'I've not

00:42:24.640 --> 00:42:26.550
forgotten the underground churches in

00:42:26.560 --> 00:42:29.190
China and Iran. There will be a major

00:42:29.200 --> 00:42:32.150
harvest of souls. All this disruption is

00:42:32.160 --> 00:42:33.589
