00:42:33.599 --> 00:42:35.430
said, 'In the underground churches

00:42:35.440 --> 00:42:37.430
and even in Iran, Brandon, there's a

00:42:37.440 --> 00:42:39.589
major harvest and there will be a major

00:42:39.599 --> 00:42:44.309
outpouring of my spirit in

00:42:44.309 --> 00:42:44.319
Iran.'I'm

00:42:44.319 --> 00:42:47.430
ignorant to the culture, folks. I'm

00:42:47.440 --> 00:42:49.270
ignorant to it. That's why I said, 'I

00:42:49.280 --> 00:42:50.790
don't know what this tarp is on their

00:42:50.800 --> 00:42:52.150
heads. I don't understand all this

00:42:52.150 --> 00:42:52.160
stuff.'I'm

00:42:52.160 --> 00:42:54.069
just, you know, a country boy

00:42:54.079 --> 00:42:56.470
from Oklahoma. But I'm telling you,

00:42:56.480 --> 00:42:58.150
I see these

00:42:58.160 --> 00:42:59.589
women, but I don't know. They have tarps

00:42:59.599 --> 00:43:01.910
