00:43:01.920 --> 00:43:04.230
the Lord on them.

00:43:04.240 --> 00:43:05.990
And they were repenting and turning away

00:43:06.000 --> 00:43:08.069
from what they knew. And they're coming

00:43:08.079 --> 00:43:10.309
to Jesus

00:43:10.319 --> 00:43:13.349
by the tens of thousands. And it's time

00:43:13.359 --> 00:43:15.670
for America to be that great pillar in

00:43:15.670 --> 00:43:15.680
these

00:43:15.680 --> 00:43:17.270
end times, and not be the people

00:43:17.280 --> 00:43:18.470
going, 'Well, you know, I don't

00:43:18.480 --> 00:43:20.069
know if America's in or America's

00:43:20.069 --> 00:43:20.079
out.'But

00:43:20.079 --> 00:43:22.069
I'm telling you, from what I hear,

00:43:22.079 --> 00:43:24.230
great revival is already taking place in

00:43:24.240 --> 00:43:26.230
some of these places in Africa and some

00:43:26.240 --> 00:43:28.150
of these places in the Middle East. And

00:43:28.160 --> 00:43:29.589
people are going, 'We're already

00:43:29.599 --> 00:43:31.829
seeing revival, Brandon. Where are you

00:43:31.839 --> 00:43:34.230
all at?'And I'm like, 'Oh, I'm jealous

00:43:34.240 --> 00:43:37.030
of it. Are you serious?

00:43:37.040 --> 00:43:38.390
You're here, you're having

00:43:38.390 --> 00:43:38.400
revival.'Because

00:43:38.400 --> 00:43:41.430
as our channel grows and we're

00:43:41.440 --> 00:43:42.710
on these other—we have seven other

00:43:42.720 --> 00:43:45.109
channels. Seven other channels. All to

00:43:45.119 --> 00:43:48.069
the glory of God. Seven other channels.

