computer because we don't know Chinese or we

00:43:54.960 --> 00:43:57.510
don't know Korean. But they think we

00:43:57.520 --> 00:43:59.349
do, and it's awesome. I'm just like,

00:43:59.359 --> 00:44:01.510
'Praise God.'Yeah, they say, 'You

00:44:01.510 --> 00:44:01.520
learned

00:44:01.520 --> 00:44:03.270
Chinese.

00:44:03.280 --> 00:44:05.589
You're speaking good

00:44:05.589 --> 00:44:05.599
Chinese.'It's

00:44:05.599 --> 00:44:08.309
just a blessing. But they're asking

00:44:08.319 --> 00:44:10.150
for Bibles.

00:44:10.160 --> 00:44:11.829
They're here in America, some of them,

00:44:11.839 --> 00:44:13.109
and they're saying, 'Please, can you

00:44:13.119 --> 00:44:17.270
help us?'Of course we can. We would

00:44:17.280 --> 00:44:20.390
love to help you. Don't take for

00:44:20.390 --> 00:44:20.400
granted our freedoms.

